data.description: Lovely two story home on a beautiful corner lot in a lake community just minutes from Highway 20 and I 75. The main living area was remodeled in 2023 opening up to a spacious living room with a fireplace to relax by in those cold winter nights or spend some time on the screened in porch listening to some tunes. The separate formal dining room leads in to the nice sized kitchen with granite counter tops, island for extra prep space, and a walk in pantry. Up the staircase there is a private owner's suite with a spacious walk- in closet, separate soaking tub and shower and a private water closet. There are 3 additional bedrooms, full bath, and laundry space. basement has an office, media room, full bath, bonus room, and unfinished space for storage. It also has a terrace level covered patio. ( New Roof with 30 year warranty) Don't miss out on what could be your forever home!
